    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>remaining chilli flakes </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!), <strong>fish sauce </strong>with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Add a squeeze of your <strong>lime juice</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>prik nam pla</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
